ygData.messageBody:
Salutations Sindaani!

I'm a bit behind on my e-mail so I just got the notice
and wanted to send you a bit of a greeting and welcome
to the list.

I'm still relatively new to EQ. I have a lvl 27 Wood
Elf Ranger on Xegony and a lvl 2 bard on Cazic Thule.
Both go by the name of Brangvyne but I don't play the
Bard much.

Nice to see you here and feel free to post, it gets
slow around here sometimes.

:o)
Bran
lvl 27 Wood Elf Ranger
